    "body": "I think we should be using `posix_spawn` here. It will mean we have to set `CLOEXEC` instead of closing files after a `fork`, but we should be doing that anyway (`node.js` does this, so `libuv` might already be getting us most of the way there). I'm going to close this because we should have a cross-platform solution.\n",
